t-2024-07-19/</link><description>智利主要锂产区发生强烈地震后，中国锂价周五反弹，尽管日益增长的需求担忧打压了用于电动汽车电池的金属。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 11:04:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-lithium-rebounds-chile-earthquake-demand-concerns-persist-2024-07-19/</guid></item><item><title>克里姆林宫表示，俄罗斯军事代表团正在朝鲜帮助执行普京达成的协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russian-military-delegation-is-north-korea-help-implement-agreements-reached-by-2024-07-19/</link><description>克里姆林宫发言人德米特里·佩斯科夫周五表示，俄罗斯军事代表团正在朝鲜，致力于执行弗拉基米尔·普京总统最近访问平壤期间达成的协议。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 10:55:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russian-military-delegation-is-north-korea-help-implement-agreements-reached-by-2024-07-19/</guid></item><item><title>中国石化上半年原油吞吐量仅增长0.1%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinas-sinopec-reports-first-half-crude-throughput-up-only-01-2024-07-19/</link><description>亚洲最大的炼油企业中国石油化工股份有限公司（中石化）周五公布上半年原油吞吐量同比变化不大。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 10:17:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinas-sinopec-reports-first-half-crude-throughput-up-only-01-2024-07-19/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：波动性重新出现，技术中断令人烦恼</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-07-19/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 10:09:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-07-19/</guid></item><item><title>大众汽车首席执行官在北京与中国部长讨论贸易和技术</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/vw-ceo-talks-trade-tech-with-chinese-ministers-beijing-2024-07-19/</link><description>根据各部委和大众汽车的声明，大众汽车首席执行官周五在与中国工商部长的会议上讨论了自由和公平贸易、全球经济和技术。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 09:59:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/vw-ceo-talks-trade-tech-with-chinese-ministers-beijing-2024-07-19/</guid></item><item><title>大众汽车CEO：与中国部长讨论自由贸易、全球经济、人工智能</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-ceo-discussed-free-trade-global-economy-ai-with-chinese-ministers-2024-07-19/</link><description>大众汽车表示，大众汽车首席执行官奥利弗·布鲁姆在周五与中国政府部长的会议上谈到了使用人工智能和自动驾驶等技术的框架条件以及自由和公平贸易的重要性。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 09:40:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-ceo-discussed-free-trade-global-economy-ai-with-chinese-ministers-2024-07-19/</guid></item><item><title>国务院副总理将出席中俄能源合作委员会会议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-vice-premier-attend-china-russia-energy-cooperation-committee-meeting-2024-07-19/</link><description>外交部周五表示，中国国务院副总理丁薛祥将于7月21日至23日出席中俄能源合作委员会第二十一次会议和第六届中俄能源商务论坛。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 07:56:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-vice-premier-attend-china-russia-energy-cooperation-committee-meeting-2024-07-19/</guid></item><item><title>新加坡命令社交媒体公司封锁与流亡中国商人有关的 95 个账户</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/singapore-orders-social-media-firms-block-95-accounts-tied-exiled-chinese-2024-07-19/</link><description>新加坡政府周五表示，已下令五个社交媒体平台阻止该城市国家的用户访问 95 个账户，这些账户大多与流亡中国大亨郭文贵有关。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 07:44:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/singapore-orders-social-media-firms-block-95-accounts-tied-exiled-chinese-2024-07-19/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示，即使经济放缓，中国也可能维持贷款利率不变</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-likely-maintain-lending-rates-even-economy-slows-2024-07-19/</link><description>路透调查显示，预计中国周一将维持基准贷款利率不变，而更多市场参与者预计，在第二季度经济数据弱于预期后，将进一步放松货币政策以援助经济。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 07:27:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-likely-maintain-lending-rates-even-economy-slows-2024-07-19/</guid></item><item><title>焦点：贸易紧张局势加剧，中国风力涡轮机制造商进军欧洲</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/climate-energy/chinese-wind-turbine-makers-move-into-europe-trade-tensions-flare-2024-07-19/</link><description>中国风力涡轮机制造商本月在德国获得了第一笔订单，他们在欧洲市场上建立了势头，并加剧了欧盟行业对其面临生存威胁的担忧。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 06:04:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/climate-energy/chinese-wind-turbine-makers-move-into-europe-trade-tensions-flare-2024-07-19/</guid></item><item><title>国际能源署表示，今年冷却需求的增长将使燃煤电厂保持在线状态</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/rising-cooling-demand-keep-coal-plants-online-this-year-iea-says-2024-07-19/</link><description>国际能源署 (IEA) 在周五的一份报告中表示，由于气温上升，空调需求增加，今年全球电力需求将以近 20 年来最快的速度增长。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 05:43:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/rising-cooling-demand-keep-coal-plants-online-this-year-iea-says-2024-07-19/</guid></item><item><title>尽管中国经济发展缓慢，电梯制造商的订单量仍保持增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/schindler-order-intake-slips-second-quarter-weighed-by-china-2024-07-19/</link><description>欧洲电梯制造商迅达和通力周五公布的第二季度订单量超出预期，但警告称中国建筑业放缓正在拖累新安装量。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 04:58:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/schindler-order-intake-slips-second-quarter-weighed-by-china-2024-07-19/</guid></item></channel></rss>